      <title>加拿大央行再次将利率降至 4.25%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-04/bank-of-canada-cuts-rates-again-to-4-25</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大央行再次降息，并表示未来可能进一步降息。以行长蒂芙·麦克勒姆为首的政策制定者将基准隔夜利率下调至 4.25%。他表示，如果通胀继续放缓，预期进一步宽松是“合理的”。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-04/bank-of-canada-cuts-rates-again-to-4-25</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 15:58:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿波罗计划建立私人信贷贷款交易部门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/apollo-plans-to-build-out-trading-desk-for-private-credit-loans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，阿波罗全球管理公司 (Apollo Global Management Inc.) 正计划建立一个二级交易平台，为少数贷方提供的私人债务提供资金。由于细节属于保密，该知情人士不愿透露姓名。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/apollo-plans-to-build-out-trading-desk-for-private-credit-loans</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 15:55:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市政债券市场大型交易热潮没有停止的迹象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/muni-bond-market-boom-in-mega-deals-shows-no-sign-of-stopping</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年已是市政债券销售创纪录的一年，超大规模交易（超过 10 亿美元）的持续发展步伐丝毫没有放缓的迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/muni-bond-market-boom-in-mega-deals-shows-no-sign-of-stopping</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 15:47:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受美国数据支撑美联储降息预期，日元兑美元上涨 1%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/yen-climbs-1-versus-dollar-as-us-data-supports-bets-on-fed-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国劳动力市场降温的新迹象增强了美联储在未来几个月进一步大幅降息的理由，日元兑美元汇率周三一度飙升逾 1%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/yen-climbs-1-versus-dollar-as-us-data-supports-bets-on-fed-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 14:53:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西班牙选择埃斯克里瓦部长领导央行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/spain-picks-minister-jose-luis-escriva-to-lead-the-central-bank</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙政府部长何塞·路易斯·埃斯克里瓦 (Jose Luis Escriva) 被选为该国央行行长，以参与欧元区下周可能做出的降息决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/spain-picks-minister-jose-luis-escriva-to-lead-the-central-bank</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 13:25:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>天气转好带来新作物供应希望，可可价格下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/coffee-rises-as-traders-eye-stockpiles-drop-and-brazil-s-weather</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场乐观地认为即将到来的主要作物收获将为全球市场带来更多供应，可可期货跌至 8 月 8 日以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/coffee-rises-as-traders-eye-stockpiles-drop-and-brazil-s-weather</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 12:31:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经济降温 美国债券波动率将超越欧洲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/bond-volatility-in-us-eclipses-europe-as-recession-angst-rises</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有迹象表明，全球最大经济体美国正在衰退，债券交易员正准备应对比欧洲更剧烈的市场波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/bond-volatility-in-us-eclipses-europe-as-recession-angst-rises</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 10:22:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球经济担忧导致欧洲股市科技股下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/european-stock-futures-drop-on-us-economy-fears-before-jobs-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对全球经济健康状况的担忧削弱了本周晚些时候美国关键就业数据公布前的市场人气，欧洲股市下跌。科技股下跌，追随英伟达公司隔夜下跌的脚步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/european-stock-futures-drop-on-us-economy-fears-before-jobs-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 05:46:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券交易员在 JOLTS 之后重新押注美联储降息：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数据显示美国劳动力市场进一步放缓，引发华尔街对美联储降息的押注，导致美国国债收益率暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 22:37:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度官员将 Byju 的贷方从债权人小组中除名</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/byju-s-lenders-kicked-off-creditor-panel-by-india-court-official</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度法院指定的仲裁员将 Byju’s 的美国债权人从有影响力的债权人委员会中剔除，对于陷入困境的在线教育公司来说，这是对试图收回超过 12 亿美元债务的债权人的胜利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/byju-s-lenders-kicked-off-creditor-panel-by-india-court-official</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 21:57:55 GMT</pubDate>
